| 1 | 🔴 Critical | No authentication on `/users` | JWT/session middleware |
| 2 | 🔴 Critical | Missing security headers | `helmet` |
| 3 | 🔴 High | No rate limiting | `express-rate-limit` |
| 4 | 🟠 High | No body parser / size limits | `express.json({ limit })` |
| 5 | 🟠 High | No input validation | `express-validator` |
| 6 | 🟠 Medium | No CORS policy | `cors` with allowlist |
