| 8 | 🟡 Low | Timestamp in health endpoint | Return `{ status: 'ok' }` only |
| 9 | 🟡 Low | Email in list response | Field projection / data minimization |
| 10 | 🟡 Low | No HTTPS enforcement | TLS termination + HSTS |

